extendedInfo.description: A Simple Calculator to help you compare two different Interest Rates and get a set of results like:- Total Amount Saved from Any Amount at start, Monthly Intended Savings and Number of Saving Years- Total Interests earned from the two Interest Rates- Total Savings Accumulated (a sum of the above two)- Difference in Savings madeUse this piece of information to help you appreciate how much more money you can make by exploring plans that can give you higher interest rates.
